style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iXzffn kEIevs pf-254_"><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-255_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Hepha app is suitable for the HEPHA Trekking 7 e-bike. If you wish, you can view all the technical data of the e-bike here:<br></p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-257_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><a href="//pages/trekking-7-overview" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span>https://hepha.com/pages/trekking-7-overview</a></p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-259_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You can download the free Hepha APP from the Google Play Store or APP Store.<br></p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-261_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hepha" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hepha</a></p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-263_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/hepha/id1622732474" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span>https://apps.apple.com/app/hepha/id1622732474</a></p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-265_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Password: Use at least 8 characters, including uppercase and lowercase letters, and numbers. After you have entered your password, you will receive a confirmation email. You should click on the link in the email.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-cbekWb cpUCMD pf-267_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-bklkYA kzHulO pf-268_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="440d6f8e-695f-48a3-88ca-95fd45bc0800" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Bluetooth Connection / E-Bike Registration</span></div></summary><div class="sc-fGdjyZ eeuPoR pf-270_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-hbKfhP esHkbO pf-271_"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-272_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iXzffn kEIevs pf-273_"><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-274_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Please log into the Hepha APP and scan the QR code on the back of the manual to register your e-bike.</p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-276_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">1) Connect your smartphone to the Hepha display on the e-bike via Bluetooth.Stay close to the e-bike while connecting to Bluetooth. If the Bluetooth logo is gray, Bluetooth is turned off.<br><br>If the Bluetooth logo is bold black, Bluetooth is on but not connected. If the Bluetooth logo is blue, the Bluetooth connection has been successfully established.</p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-278_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">2) The battery level in the app is the same as on the display, and the icon is green. The display automatically shows the current time.</p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-280_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">3) Currently, the total kilometers can only be viewed through the app (the total kilometers cannot be read on the display).</p><p class="sc-brPMkR piylR pf-282_ pf-text-1" 